other_tests.findings: Cholelithiasis without gallbladder wall thickening; hepatic parenchyma within normal limits; smooth contour of liver; no focal liver mass; main portal vein patent with hepatopetal flow; no ascites; no intrahepatic biliary dilation; common hepatic duct diameter 6 mm; pancreas appears within normal limits; normal echogenicity of spleen with length 10.5 cm; limited views of kidneys show no hydronephrosis; visualized portions of aorta and IVC within normal limits.
